@startuml
title SearchRec Overall Architecture
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "BusinessSystem" as BusinessSystem
rectangle "app_searchrec.views\n(SearchRec*View)" as SearchRecAPI
rectangle "SearchRecService\n(search / recommend / rank)" as SearchRecService

package "Adapters" as adapters {
  rectangle "IndexAdapter\n(build_index_adapter)" as IndexAdapter
  rectangle "VectorAdapter\n(build_vector_adapter)" as VectorAdapter
  rectangle "FeatureStoreAdapter\n(build_feature_store_adapter)" as FeatureAdapter
}

package "providers\n(app_searchrec.providers)" as providers_pkg {
  rectangle "SimpleTextEmbeddingProvider\n(embedding_provider)" as EmbedProvider
}

package "Index backends\n(mutually exclusive)" as idx_back {
  rectangle "OpenSearchIndexAdapter" as OpenSearch
  rectangle "DbIndexAdapter\n(MySQL doc + doc_term)" as DbIndex
}

package "Vector backends\n(at most one remote)" as vec_back {
  rectangle "DbVectorAdapter" as DbVector
  rectangle "MilvusVectorAdapter" as Milvus
  rectangle "QdrantVectorAdapter" as Qdrant
}

package "Feature backends" as feat_back {
  rectangle "DbFeatureStoreAdapter" as DbFeature
  rectangle "FeastFeatureStoreAdapter" as Feast
}

BusinessSystem --> SearchRecAPI : HTTP API
SearchRecAPI --> SearchRecService

SearchRecService --> IndexAdapter : search, upsert,\nget_document
SearchRecService --> VectorAdapter : search, upsert
SearchRecService --> FeatureAdapter : upsert,\nget_doc_features,\nget_user_features

note bottom of SearchRecService
  **Fusion scoring** (lexical + vector blend + tags + popularity)
  × **score_boost** (Feast / memory features first, else index row)
  is implemented inside **SearchRecService.search**.
  **rank** recomputes **final_score** from caller-supplied
  base_score / ctr_score / freshness_score only — **no adapter I/O**.
end note

IndexAdapter --> OpenSearch : SEARCHREC_OPENSEARCH_ENABLED
IndexAdapter --> DbIndex : else (default)

VectorAdapter --> Milvus : SEARCHREC_MILVUS_ENABLED
VectorAdapter --> Qdrant : else if SEARCHREC_QDRANT_ENABLED
VectorAdapter --> DbVector : else (default)

FeatureAdapter --> Feast : SEARCHREC_FEAST_ENABLED
FeatureAdapter --> DbFeature : else (default)

Qdrant ..> EmbedProvider : upsert & search:\nencode text → vector
note bottom of Milvus
  Remote service receives query/documents;\nno local embedding in this app.
end note

@enduml
